{
  "stem": "20684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everyone seems to be going that way, towards east, east, whoever could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- we joined a-- the march east.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- we went on for a few days, and there was explosions still heard far behind us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went and went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think days and nights, maybe two, three days, two, three nights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't be sure because my mother has never spoken about this, and no one else knows, because my father perished, of course, during the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it's my recollection that-- but days and nights could have been not as long as-- but it seemed like days and nights.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We covered something maybe like 200, 300 kilometers, so maybe it wasn't all that many days and too many nights.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Until we got across the river Bug, which was separating the German half of Poland to the Russian half of Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we actually went east towards the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and that's where we-- life settled again to-- to some normality, but different to what it was before.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father still worked as a doctor, but he was now a military doctor, military hospital, the Russian military hospital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't see much of him either then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were more people, in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were more people than we here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we just had a big large house for just the three of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here there were more people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were other families, I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Another friend of his was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a dentist, and his wife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then my auntie came with her boyfriend, and my father married them, because they weren't married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was rather young, I think, 20 or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
